DESCRIPTION:<p>What roles do artists play in civil society? What do arti\n\
	nhttps://townhallseattle.org/event/this-art-here/\n\nFrom City of Seattle 
	— Office of Arts & Cultural Affairs
URL:https://townhallseattle.org/event/this-art-here/
